Owner_FirstName.RulesforWizard: If Owner_Type = Individual,Joint then Default = Blank;If Owner_Type = Individual,Joint then display,enable else Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation then disable,hide
Owner_FirstName.ValidationRules: If Owner_Type = Individual,Joint and Owner_FirstName = blank then Issue Error Message: Owner First Name is required.

Owner_TIN.RulesforWizard: If Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation then Default = Blank;If Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation then display,enable, else Owner_Type = Individual,Joint then disable,hide
Owner_TIN.ValidationRules: If Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation and Owner_TIN = blank then Issue Error Message: Owner TIN is required.;If Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation and Owner_TIN = Invalid then Issue Error Message: Please enter a valid TIN for Owner.
